                                    </div>
                                    <div class="hh1 text-primary mt-3"><i class="fa fa-star text-warning"></i>&nbsp;DALAL Service Features</div>
                                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                        <li><i class="fa fa-check text-primary"></i>&nbsp;Qualified and hourly workers</li>
                                        <li><i class="fa fa-check text-primary"></i>&nbsp;Matches your needs</li>
                                        <li><i class="fa fa-check text-primary"></i>&nbsp;At an appropriate cost</li>
                                        <li><i class="fa fa-check text-primary"></i>&nbsp;In a manner that respects your privacy and the nature of Saudi society</li>
                                        <li><i class="fa fa-check text-primary"></i>&nbsp;Ensures that the service is delivered to your site at the time that suits you</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col">

                                    <div class="alert alert-light text-center rounded-20px border p-5 mt-3">
                                        <div class="clearfix"><img src="~/Images/frontEnd/family.jpg" alt="Only families" /></div>
